  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The user can summon any number of sharks to a maximum of one per two levels of the user. Each frilled shark in the school is proficient with whatever weapon it spawns with and has a 1d4 bite attack if disarmed. They can move 30 ft. in a round, have 6 HP, 12 AC, +1 to all saves, and +1 attack bonus with no other bonuses to speak of. They are small and can only perform basic movements and attacks, being fairly unintelligent and untrained in anything more advanced.<br><br>Each shark is summoned with a random weapon from the following chart:<br><br>Dagger<br><br>Kodachi<br><br>Kama<br><br>Knuckle Blade<br><br>Shortsword<br><br>Katana<br><br>Sabre<br><br>Hand Scythe</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Blood Pact (Sharks) (f) and Kuchiyose no Jutsu (t)</p>\n<p><b>Effect:</b> Up to 1 Summoned Shark per 2 levels</p>\n<p><b>Expendable Component:</b> Expendable Component -Some of the user's blood and a summoning scroll for the Shark blood pact.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third and fifth step of mastery grant a +1 bonus to the school of sharks' HP, AC, Saves, Attack, and Damage.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
